name: Lace Inspired Midi Ring
description:
This ring is really cool! You can turn the ring upside down or to the side and there will be a different look to it. It's like owning 5 different rings. This design is a metal casting that Is inspired by vintage lace. Very unique! 

This ring is made in a size 2 1/2 ( your standard first knuckle ring size). It can be sized to a 3 or 4 upon Request.

Made in brass. Special orders of silver or 14k are available upon request, but prices may vary.

name: Woman's Hand Crafted Bolo Tie
description:
Hand crafted brass bolo tie. The pendant is adjustable on a genuine leather chord. The leather is finished with brass tubing and beads. The leather measures at 36 inches. Pendant measures at 1 3/4 inches long. 

Available as a special order in sterling silver and 10k gold. For special orders please message me.

name: Carved Triangle Pendant
description:
Brass pendant with zig zag carving. The pendant is oxidized and then hand polished to show a variety of different tones. The chain is made out of solid brass and measure at 34 inches. The pendant itself if 3 1/2 inches. This is a stand out piece!

Special orders for Sterling silver or 10k gold available upon requests. Prices for special orders will vary.  Contact me if interested.

name: Oxidized Tribal Pendant
description:
Flat Brass pendant cut out with tribal design. The pendant is oxidized and come on a 34 inch solid brass chain. Hand made, and hand polished.  The pendant measure to be 2 3/4 inches long and 2 1/2 inches wide.  This is a show stopping necklace! 

This necklace is also available without the oxidation.

name: Triangle in Triangle Ring
description:
This ring is made out of solid brass and is hand polished.  This casting   is oxidized for color enhancement. There is a hand carved triangle inverted inside of the Triangle.  The triangle measures at 3/4 of an inch.

Available in sizes 6 and 7

Special order for sterling silver and 10K gold are available upon request.  Prices may vary for special orders.
